> + *
> + *  +---+-------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
> + *  |   | Bits  | Description                                                  |
> + *  +===+=======+==============================================================+
> + *  | 0 |    31 | ORIGIN                                                       |
> + *  |   +-------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
> + *  |   | 30:28 | TYPE = GUC_HXG_TYPE_RESPONSE_FAILURE_                        |
> + *  |   +-------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
> + *  |   | 27:16 | **HINT** - additional error hint                             |
> + *  |   +-------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
> + *  |   |  15:0 | **ERROR** - error/result code                                |
> + *  +---+-------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
> + */
> +
> +#define GUC_HXG_FAILURE_MSG_LEN			GUC_HXG_MSG_MIN_LEN
